high_descs: Turn around and walk between the stove and the kitchen island to get to the middle of the kitchen island, on your right.
Pick up the knife on the island closest to the loaf of bread.
Turn to your left and walk to the end of the island where you will turn right, and go to the kitchen sink on your left.
Put the knife in the measuring cup, underneath the right side of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the measuring cup with the knife inside it.
Step up to the sink in front of you.
Place the measuring cup with the knife inside it, in the sink, on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Put a measuring cup containing a knife in the sink.

high_descs: Move right then right again facing the kitchen island counter on the right
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle on the counter top
Carry the knife over to the kitchen sink cupboard on the right side under the sink
Open the cupboard and place the knife inside of the cup in the cupboard
Pick up the cup with the knife then close the cupboard
Move towards the sink then face the sink
Place the mug with the knife with the knife inside of it in the sink basin on the far left
anns.task_desc: Move a knife in a mug to the sink

high_descs: Turn around and turn to the right to face the knives on the brown counter.
Pick up the knife on the right.
Go left and turn right and then turn to the left to face the sink.
Open the cupboard below the sink and to the right and put the knife in the glass.
Pick the glass up from the lower cupboard.
Stand up to face the sink.
Put the glass in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a knife in it in the sink.
